.Ve
.Sh "getSubjects"
.IX Subsection "getSubjects"
Returns information from every subject into a hash array
Fields in each hash returned are name, owner, description, and subject type
.PP
Here is a definition of the different subject types
.PP
1. Standard \s-1MRC\s0 converged (Bugeco/requirement/feature etc)
2. System Internal to \s-1ES\s0
3. Custom Any subject created by a custom which is not \s-1MRC\s0
4. Built in Created by \s-1ES\s0 team. Such as baseline, url, comments etc
